OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny patchy fog and low cloud
OL,6,Fwill clear quickly to give a fine day
OL,7,Fwith plenty of sunshine.
OL,8,
OL,9,CTonight:FAfter a mostly clear start,
OL,10,Fpatchy low cloud will develop later in
OL,11,Fthe night, along with areas of mist
OL,12,Fand fog. Chilly, with an isolated
OL,13,Ffrost possible.
OL,14,
OL,15,CThursday:FPatchy early low cloud, mist
OL,16,Fand fog will soon clear to give
OL,17,Fanother fine and dry day with long
OL,18,Fsunny spells. Mild inland, but cooler
OL,19,Ftowards the east coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
